descript.purpose: Data set represents the official street centerline network of San Francisco. When used for geocoding, users should select for the Street Name and Street Type, the fields "STREET" and "ST_TYPE", respectively. Be sure not to use the field "STREETNAME" , it is a concatentation of the name and type of the street.
